<br>
As I was travelling through Oasis, I saw this &lt;cough&gt; Wizard and saw the boots he had that made him move VERY fast. I decided that I wanted these boots for myself. I had run up to the wizard you was immediatly scared out of his mind...him being so weak, me so unbelievably powerful. He tried to cast his feeble spells, to no avail. He tried to run but felt the might of my axe as it cleaved him over and over. And as I was wiping the blood of my axe, I tried to take these boots, only to see they were glued to his feet. I softly cursed as I mummbled, &quot;At least another wizard dead...&quot;<br>
